Brown: Heh, I'm finally{nl}
getting into it.{waitkey}From here on, I'll show you{nl}
what the great Brown can do!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Uesugi seems to have{nl}
already forgotten he was{nl}
rescued.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Don't you think{nl}
Sonomura's acting strange?{nl}
Hmm...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Is it really okay to{nl}
keep the store open?{waitkey}Don't blame me if a demon{nl}
gets you!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Come to think of it,{nl}
I've heard of that odd shop{nl}
before too.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: It really is odd that{nl}
the shop would open at a time{nl}
